stringStats.value: The Virindi are a mysterious race of levitating beings shrouded by heavy cloaks. Their faces -- if they have faces at all -- are concealed by grotesque, white masks. No one has seen a Virindi without its cloak or mask. Little is known of their intentions, but they are very powerful and capricious, and are potent magic-users. They also wield fearsome sickles, swinging them with unnatural speed. Most reported sightings thus far have been in the Direlands.
